{{Quote|Intelligence will hold the New Republic together, or the New Republic won't hold at all.|[[Caern Adan]]|<ref name="Alphabet Squadron" />}}
'''New Republic Intelligence''' was the primary Intelligence agency of the [[New Republic]].

==History==
{{Quote|Alliance–Excuse me. ''New Republic'' Intelligence.|Caern Adan, to Yrica Quell|<ref name="Alphabet Squadron" />}}
New Republic Intelligence was the successor to the [[Rebel Alliance Intelligence Service]].<ref name="On the Front Lines" /> Following the [[Battle of Endor]] and the establishment of the [[New Republic]], the new government established its own intelligence division, which was headed by [[Chief of Intelligence|Chief]] [[Airen Cracken]].<ref name="Alphabet Squadron" /> [[Gallius Rax]] leaked early reports of an [[Imperial Navy|Imperial fleet]] gathering at [[Jakku]], knowing the news would reach New Republic Intelligence.<ref name="On the Front Lines" />

